                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-1">Real-world AI tool evaluations</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">from SMB practitioners who've actually tested them in similar business environments</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-accent-cyan-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-1">Strategic pilot design workshops</h4>
                  <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">so you can avoid expensive AI experiments that don't deliver measurable results</p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-accent-cyan-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-1">Risk management frameworks</h4>
